---
title: Honey Garlic Chicken Breast Wraps with Potato Wedges and Ranch
description: Pub food at its finest, from the comfort of your own home! These wraps are sure to be a hit with the whole family. And what better way to sneak some veggies into dinner than by putting them in a wrap with that classic honey-garlic flavour?!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-garlic-chicken-breast-wraps-1e6aa37e.jpg
